00077 void CHPDataTest::ChipSumTest()
00078 {
00079         CHPData data;
00080         data.AddChipSum(L"param1", L"value");
00081         data.AddChipSum(L"param2", 1);
00082         data.AddChipSum(L"param3", 123.321f);
00083 
00084         ParameterNameValueType p = data.GetChipSum(L"param1");
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.GetName() == L"param1");
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.GetValueText() == L"value");
00087 
00088         p = data.GetChipSum(L"param2");
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.GetName() == L"param2");
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00091 
00092         p = data.GetChipSum(L"param3");
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(p.GetName() == L"param3");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(p.GetValueFloat(), 123.321, 0.001f);
00095 }
